## GSP

The [GDS Supported Platform] (https://github.com/alphagov/gsp) contains various kubernetes deployments that will be useful in Connect, and where possible Connect will use the helm charts from there.

## Terraform Helm provider

The terraform provider for helm (2) which can work with charts local to the terraform repository, or remote charts. It is likely that
the best setup would be to have a chart repository, possibly via S3, and charts that are required for deployment are stored there.

Mixing the charts into the terrraform repository makes it harder to use helm directly if required.

https://github.com/dumrauf/s3-helm-chart-repo-with-docs looks like a useful place to start looking at this

